div.p:
To make it so that different types of valves can be developed and implemented into the existing code easily, the actual code only communicates with a valve through an interface. Any type of valve must therefore be a sub-class of IValve to slot into the calculation scheme.
Currently, ReedValve is implemented. This valve contains an FEM to model its deflection.
